### RestQL Echo + GORM API
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Get all users
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

### Filter by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?filter=status='active'

### Comparison operators
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?filter=age>=25

### LIKE operator
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?filter=name~'Silva'

### IN operator
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?filter=status IN ['active','pending']

### AND operator
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?filter=status='active'&&age>25

### OR operator
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?filter=status='active'||status='pending'

### Complex filters with grouping
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?filter=(status='active'&&age>25)||(status='pending'&&age>30)

### Select specific fields
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?fields=id,name,email

### Sort results
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?sort=-created_at,name

### Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?limit=5&offset=0

### Complete example with all features
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?fields=id,name,email,status,age&filter=status='active'&&age>=25&sort=-age&limit=10&offset=0

